    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Integration Points\n\n**HEBELING OS → n8n**\nWebhook trigger with manuscript metadata\n\n**n8n → Supabase**\n- Project creation\n- File storage\n- Stage tracking\n\n**n8n → Notifications**\n- Slack (team)\n- Gmail (author)\n\n**Response → HEBELING OS**\nProject ID + tracking URL",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "f90680b4-5cf8-4917-9949-aacb8516302d",
      "name": "Sticky Note 4ce61df4",
