        "message": "=Dear {{ $(\"Manuscript Upload Webhook\").item.json.body.author_name }},\n\nThank you for submitting your manuscript \"{{ $(\"Create Project Record\").item.json.title }}\" to Reino Editorial through HEBELING OS.\n\n✅ Your manuscript has been successfully received and your editorial project has been initialized.\n\n📋 Project Details:\n• Project ID: {{ $(\"Create Project Record\").item.json.id }}\n• Service Plan: {{ $(\"Manuscript Upload Webhook\").item.json.body.service_plan }}\n• Editorial Style: {{ $(\"Manuscript Upload Webhook\").item.json.body.editorial_style }}\n• Trim Size: {{ $(\"Manuscript Upload Webhook\").item.json.body.trim_size }}\n\n🔄 Next Steps:\nYour manuscript will now enter our 12-day editorial process. You can track progress in real-time through your HEBELING OS client portal.\n\nThe editorial team will begin content parsing and diagnostic analysis within 24 hours.\n\nThank you for choosing Reino Editorial!\n\nThe HEBELING OS Team",
